  password-based authentication system for the admin dashboard. Initially, a
  custom session management system was built, but it was later simplified to use
  Next.js middleware for more efficient route protection and a basic
  authentication cookie. The outcome is a functional backend for data storage
  and a basic admin interface, with the database setup and authentication
  confirmed.
